        <Parent_String>Alpine skiing [300239498], skiing [300222781], ice and snow activities [300239454], physical activities by location [300239664], physical activities by specific context [300239444], physical activities [300222722], Physical and Mental Activities (hierarchy name) [300222468], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
